criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Written consent;

          2. Age ≥ 10 years;

          3. Eastern Cooperative Oncology Group Performance status ≤ 2;

          4. Histologically confirmed desmoid tumor;

          5. Disease progression after local treatment

          6. Measurable target lesion (RECIST criteria) ;

          7. Adequate hematological, renal and liver functions :

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Other co-existing malignancies or malignancies diagnosed within the last 5 years with
             the exception of basal cell carcinoma or cervical cancer in situ.

          2. Pregnant or lactating female

          3. Evidence of any other significant clinical disorder or laboratory finding that makes
             it undesirable for the patient to participate in the study
